<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218721>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Polycirrus papillosus sp. nov. Photos A – C, E from holotype (MZUSP 1216); photos D, F – G from paratype 10 (MZUSP 1244). A, notochaetae from anterior notopodium; B, close up view of the tips of two notochaetae from anterior row (winged); C – E, uncini, anterior neuropodium; F – G, uncini, posterior neuropodia; arrow points to dorsal button. Scale bars: A – C = 20 μm; D, G = 5 μm; E = 10 μm; F = 2 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/218721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218725>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Polycirrus habitats sp. nov. Photos A – D, F from holotype (MZUSP 1221); photos E, G – I from paratype 1 (MZUSP 1246). A – B, tips of pinnate notochaetae; C – D, F – I, uncini, posterior neuropodia; E, notochaetae, anterior notopodium. Scale bars: A, C = 20 μm; B, D, F = 10 μm; E, G – I = 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/218725/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

